Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.39,0:01:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if that's true, Kira is... the second-generation L.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.42,0:01:37.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To all of you at the Japanese Investigative Headquarters: {\alpha&HFF&}have you ever thought, even once, that your "second-generation" L might be Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.91,0:01:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To all of you at the Japanese Investigative Headquarters: have you ever thought, even once, {\alpha&HFF&}that your "second-generation" L might be Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.68,0:01:43.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To all of you at the Japanese Investigative Headquarters: have you ever thought, even once, that your "second-generation" L might be Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.17,0:01:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Near... {\alpha&HFF&}I've got no choice now but to kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.42,0:01:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Near... I've got no choice now but to kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.60,0:01:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is terrible! Live on TV, Demegawa is...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.56,0:01:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, Demegawa, have finally tracked down the base of an evil organization that seeks to capture our God, Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.52,0:02:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And along with my brothers, we have them surrounded!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.01,0:02:05.06,SIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(364,334)}Transfer
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.58,0:02:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Supporters of Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.32,0:02:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't enter the building all at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.17,0:02:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The opposition may try and blend in with the crowd and escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.29,0:02:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Obey my orders as Kira's spokesman!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.21,0:02:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We must corner them, expose them to the cameras, and offer them to Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.33,0:02:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I definitely won't overlook you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.54,0:02:56.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Near... {\alpha&HFF&}for now, you'd better get out of there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.51,0:02:58.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Near... for now, you'd better get out of there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.14,0:03:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got a lot of nerve advising me, considering you're Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.20,0:03:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you're still saying that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.65,0:03:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are other organizations out there hunting Kira, and yet this attack happens immediately after I start suspecting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.48,0:03:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The timing is far too convenient.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.16,0:03:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Near, you're jumping to far too many conclusions from a misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.54,0:03:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To them members present at the Investigative Headquarters, at best, Kira is in your midst...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.66,0:03:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.12,0:03:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light-kun is Kira... {\alpha&HFF&}that idea is being reinforced yet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.04,0:03:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light-kun is Kira... that idea is being reinforced yet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.00,0:03:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The previous L also suspected Light-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.25,0:03:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First squad, break down the door and the first twenty, make your way in!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.62,0:03:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Second squad, hold!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.53,0:03:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave that to us! We're the first squad!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.04,0:03:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the--!! We were here first!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.36,0:04:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Near, unless we get out of here quickly...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.04,0:04:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What foolish people...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.10,0:04:09.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't find it strange that there are people who are willing to support Kira,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.39,0:04:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but that only applies to those that genuinely want Kira to judge criminals.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.86,0:04:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The people besieging this place are different.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.18,0:04:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are truly worthless human beings.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.32,0:04:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as they're having fun, it's all that matters... they're selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.22,0:04:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-{\alpha&HFF&}I realize that, but for now, we need to...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.69,0:04:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I realize that, but for now, we need to...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.10,0:04:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's use L's inheritance and those people we employed that oppose Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.92,0:04:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But once we use that plan...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.38,0:04:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it. The preparations have already been made.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.13,0:04:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This should be interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.05,0:05:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-{\alpha&HFF&}M-Money!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.90,0:05:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-M-{\alpha&HFF&}Money!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.78,0:05:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-M-Money!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.36,0:05:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's money!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.90,0:05:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Money?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.37,0:05:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's so much of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.76,0:05:19.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.45,0:05:22.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should have gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.66,0:05:23.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsuda...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.44,0:05:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gee, humans really are amusing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.33,0:05:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, you can exchange that stuff for apples, so I guess I can understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.43,0:05:32.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard! I got that first!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.14,0:05:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Outta the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.26,0:05:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit! Near, you're planning to escape amid the confusion, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.46,0:05:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you do, Demegawa's cameras should be able to...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.17,0:05:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Pilot! Head toward the floor where the money is coming from!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.61,0:05:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! {\alpha&HFF&}Deme-chan, what the hell do you think you're doing?! You can't buy love and peace with money!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.34,0:05:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! Deme-chan, what the hell do you think you're doing?! {\alpha&HFF&}You can't buy love and peace with money!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.84,0:05:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! Deme-chan, what the hell do you think you're doing?! You can't buy love and peace with money!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.10,0:06:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In Lower Manhattan, New York, a vast amount of dollars are...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.05,0:06:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The police squads have arrived!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.60,0:06:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Police squads?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.78,0:06:05.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As expected, given the panic that's ensued here, the police squads have arrived!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.02,0:06:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't looking good...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.30,0:06:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.09,0:06:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this precise moment, we're safe even if we walk right out the front door.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.65,0:06:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess in this kind of situation, the police had no choice but to act.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.54,0:06:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit! So this is how they're intending to counter it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.36,0:06:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll emerge, disguised as part of the police squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.88,0:06:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Telling Aizawa and the others to keep a close eye on the police is as good as telling them that I'm Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.53,0:06:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are police exiting the building!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.20,0:06:37.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.50,0:06:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's got to be among them...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.43,0:06:41.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.80,0:06:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.89,0:07:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder just how much money was involved...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.82,0:07:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsuda...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.96,0:07:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ten million dollars maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.12,0:07:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many apples is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.26,0:07:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Near!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.93,0:07:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Near?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.66,0:07:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Near.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.46,0:07:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've completed installation of communication circuits, so we thought we'd better get in touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.14,0:07:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Near, you're safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.64,0:07:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To all at the Investigative Headquarters, {\alpha&HFF&}I believe it won't be long before you each come to a definite decision regarding Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.58,0:07:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To all at the Investigative Headquarters, I believe it won't be long before you each come to a definite decision regarding Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.31,0:08:03.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The timing of this attack is as good as saying that Kira is among you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.51,0:08:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if none of you suspect the second-generation L, {\alpha&HFF&}then you're all worse than nursery school kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.21,0:08:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if none of you suspect the second-generation L, then you're all worse than nursery school kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.50,0:08:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've reinstated the phone number I gave you all a few days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.89,0:08:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Feel free to give me a call anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.32,0:08:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, I'll be waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.60,0:08:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What confidence... {\alpha&HFF&}or rather, he's being pretty aggressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.28,0:08:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What confidence... or rather, {\alpha&HFF&}he's being pretty aggressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.81,0:08:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What confidence... or rather, he's being pretty aggressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.20,0:08:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, {\alpha&HFF&}if any of you feel like you want to help Near, please go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.38,0:08:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, if any of you feel like you want to help Near, please go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.27,0:08:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Given the current situation, I won't be offended.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.75,0:08:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my belief that, ideally, the SPK and ourselves should understand and cooperate with each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.32,0:08:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Near's the one that's holding us back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.20,0:09:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I think about Deputy Chief Yagami, I don't want to suspect Light-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.20,0:09:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.02,0:09:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.46,0:09:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back. You came home tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.58,0:09:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Why are you still up?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.22,0:09:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got exams soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.09,0:09:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... Just don't work yourself too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.29,0:09:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You too, Dad, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.43,0:09:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't be surprising if someone does contact Near.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.01,0:09:59.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What matters is what follows.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.41,0:10:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I leave this even a single step too late, it could turn into an irrecoverable situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.11,0:10:10.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got to do it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.61,0:10:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! An emergency command from Light!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.47,0:10:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see now... {\alpha&HFF&}number three...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.66,0:10:22.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see now... number three...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.28,0:10:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.42,0:10:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes? Near speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.93,0:10:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm with the Japanese Investigative Headquarters. I'm Aizawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.52,0:10:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time has finally arrived... {\alpha&HFF&}this is so that I'll be completely safe, and a normal wife to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.68,0:10:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time has finally arrived... this is so that I'll be completely safe, and a normal wife to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.33,0:11:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is what Light wants... {\alpha&HFF&}for me to find true happiness in being a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.13,0:11:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is what Light wants... for me to find true happiness in being a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.31,0:11:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light, thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.20,0:11:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... {\alpha&HFF&}that's very interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.23,0:11:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... that's very interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.67,0:11:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, L detained two suspects for over 50 days, and the "13 days" rule cleared them both.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.82,0:11:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, but of course, that on its own doesn't mean that they are Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.97,0:11:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And L had no problems releasing them?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.51,0:11:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. He had Mr. Yagami, who was Chief at the time, play a trick on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.03,0:11:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Chief informed them that they had been confirmed as Kira and the second Kira, and that they were being taken to an execution chamber.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.74,0:11:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Along the way, the Chief pulled a gun on the suspects and said he'd kill Kira and then himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.84,0:11:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was believed that if they were Kira, being pushed so far, they would have killed the Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.19,0:11:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how the judgment was made.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.91,0:12:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira's quite a guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.61,0:12:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira used their detention to prove their innocence.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.66,0:12:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did the suspect offer to be detained?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.04,0:12:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to admit, Light-kun did volunteer to be detained...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.45,0:12:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they did, then this settles it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.04,0:12:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, who were these two suspects?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.76,0:12:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't tell you that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.38,0:12:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Despite this, I'm still working under L, as a member of the Japanese Investigative Headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.62,0:12:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.58,0:12:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for your valuable information.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.39,0:12:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the first time I've heard of people with the eyes of a Shinigami being able to see the names of others. That was helpful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.15,0:12:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.76,0:12:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Near, is that enough? {\alpha&HFF&}You aren't going to question him further?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.36,0:12:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Near, is that enough? You aren't going to question him further?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.52,0:12:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this point, it's best to leave things as they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.26,0:13:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, we've learned something vital.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.23,0:13:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deputy Chief Yagami and the suspect were father and child.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.36,0:13:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no other explanation for him saying "I'll kill Kira and then myself".
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.97,0:13:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thus, {\alpha&HFF&}the second-generation L, and the person I believe to be Kira, is... Yagami Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.20,0:13:19.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thus, the second-generation L, {\alpha&HFF&}and the person I believe to be Kira, is... Yagami Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.36,0:13:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thus, the second-generation L, and the person I believe to be Kira, is... {\alpha&HFF&}Yagami Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.25,0:13:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thus, the second-generation L, and the person I believe to be Kira, is... Yagami Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.53,0:13:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.03,0:13:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.61,0:13:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to be honest with you... {\alpha&HFF&}I contacted Near.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.12,0:13:41.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to be honest with you... I contacted Near.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.12,0:13:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it. {\alpha&HFF&}It's something that I encouraged myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.42,0:13:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it. It's something that I encouraged myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.45,0:13:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what did you talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.21,0:13:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... I won't ask you that. It might be strange for us to have a discussion about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.58,0:14:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to establish with absolute certainty that you're not Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.12,0:14:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry that you have to go through the same thing twice, {\alpha&HFF&}but until Kira's caught, I'd like to keep a close eye on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.46,0:14:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry that you have to go through the same thing twice, but until Kira's caught, I'd like to keep a close eye on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.91,0:14:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, but the same goes for Amane Misa. {\alpha&HFF&}I'll have to check her room.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.48,0:14:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, but the same goes for Amane Misa. I'll have to check her room.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.08,0:14:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's always the slight possibility that she has a notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.93,0:14:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute, Aizawa-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.75,0:14:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, please go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.33,0:14:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll all become witnesses to the fact that I'm not communicating with Misa in secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.48,0:14:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mogi?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.89,0:14:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want this cleared up too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.06,0:14:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light-kun not being Kira would be the best outcome, {\alpha&HFF&}but if evidence incriminating him as Kira turns up in Amane's room... then...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.52,0:14:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light-kun not being Kira would be the best outcome, but if evidence incriminating him as Kira turns up in Amane's room... {\alpha&HFF&}then...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.64,0:15:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light-kun not being Kira would be the best outcome, but if evidence incriminating him as Kira turns up in Amane's room... then...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.21,0:15:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aah! Mochii and Monchicchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.34,0:15:33.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Long time no see!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.32,0:15:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since Light never seems to come home from investigating Kira, I've got nothing to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.79,0:15:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She can't possibly have the notebook on her in that outfit...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.74,0:15:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa... there's been a report that a bomb has been planted at L's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.10,0:15:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's most likely a false alarm, but we'd like to check your apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.03,0:15:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! Is Light okay?! I better call him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.48,0:15:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't call him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.10,0:15:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.45,0:15:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light-kun is fine. {\alpha&HFF&}He's got some important business to attend to, so he sent us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.33,0:16:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light-kun is fine. He's got some important business to attend to, so he sent us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.12,0:16:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! Light loves Misa so much, he'd probably be even more worried if he heard my voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.05,0:16:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Search all you want, Aizawa... {\alpha&HFF&}you won't find the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.94,0:16:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Search all you want, Aizawa... you won't find the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.06,0:16:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want it to get awkward around here because of this...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.80,0:16:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't a friendship club. {\alpha&HFF&}Aizawa and Mogi can do as they please.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.67,0:16:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't a friendship club. Aizawa and Mogi can do as they please.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.68,0:16:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time for Kira's Realm to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.52,0:16:45.19,SILLYSIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs72\fscy0\t(0,500,\fscy100)\pos(353,431)}Kira's Realm
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.20,0:16:52.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Greetings, supporters of Kira! I am Demegawa, Kira-sama's spokesman.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.54,0:17:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Behold! The construction of Kira's Realm, named after this show, is progressing well thanks to all your support!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.97,0:17:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And once this is completed, let us all meet here, and welcome Kira-sama to his temple!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.34,0:17:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow... such bad taste...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.32,0:17:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, is everything alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.64,0:17:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Guess it was a fake report after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.84,0:17:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But as a precaution, one of us better stay here over the next few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.69,0:17:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.63,0:17:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mogi, you can go back to headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.25,0:17:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.39,0:17:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?! Mochii's not staying, but Monchicchi is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.23,0:17:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not dependable enough for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.03,0:17:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it... it's just that, without your old hairstyle, you just don't seem like Monchicchi. It's not cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.09,0:17:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mogi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.68,0:17:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.60,0:17:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You stay...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.30,0:17:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to complete Kira's Realm, we beseech you to donate a million yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.72,0:17:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like a scam to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.53,0:18:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, they're no different from a shady establishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.98,0:18:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just so unlike Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.78,0:18:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Demegawa... {\alpha&HFF&}he's acting on his own impulses... at this rate, people will start turning away...
